程序包 mint.mvc.converter

Package that contains all converters which convert java.lang.String to specified object.

请参阅: 说明

  • 接口概要 
    接口 说明
    Converter<T>
    Convert String to any given type.
  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    BooleanConverter
    Convert String to Boolean.
    ByteConverter
    Convert String to Byte.
    CharacterConverter
    Convert String to Character.
    ConverterFactory
    Factory for all converters(add string support).
    DoubleConverter
    Convert String to Double.
    FloatConverter
    Convert String to Float.
    IntegerConverter
    Convert String to Integer.
    LongConverter
    Convert String to Long.
    ShortConverter
    Convert String to Short.
